entrance just outside Sayle's complex.

32:52.804 --> 32:57.015
- His last message mentioned a virus.
- A computer virus?

32:57.225 --> 32:59.935
He was on his way to tell us,
but he never arrived.

33:00.186 --> 33:03.105
We need to get someone in there to
take a look...

33:03.523 --> 33:05.524
