in a computer magazine.

33:18.997 --> 33:21.289
Disc Drive World'. Do you ever read it?

33:21.582 --> 33:22.332
No.

33:22.792 --> 33:26.670
The first prize was a visit to
Cornwall to try out the stormbreaker.

33:26.838 --> 33:29.715
- He's due to arrive tomorrow.
- It's a PR stunt.

33:29.882 --> 33:33.385
