34:22.101 --> 34:25.437
We will give you
a telecommunications device.

34:25.772 --> 34:28.565
That, and other gadgets.

34:29.567 --> 34:31.025
I get gadgets?

34:44.081 --> 34:45.998
Come up and see the Robopets range.
Up on the third floor.

34:46.375 --> 34:48.627
- I want one!
- Yes, thank you, sir. Thank you very much.

34:48.920 --> 34:50.420
- I want one! - Thank you.

34:50.713 --> 34:52.422
