take to Cornwall.

35:00.765 --> 35:01.932
To Cornwall?

35:04.185 --> 35:05.268
Follow me.

35:10.858 --> 35:12.818
Andrea Chicken to floor three, please.
Thank you.

35:13.152 --> 35:15.070
