36:58.633 --> 37:01.092
It's to contact us,
assuming you can be bothered.

37:01.427 --> 37:06.389
This one here turns it into
a bug-finder and sonic intensifier.

37:06.599 --> 37:10.227
You can hear conversations through
solid walls for up to 250 yards.

37:10.478 --> 37:14.773
