Could you live with that, Mrs Jones?

44:57.945 --> 45:01.781
I worked for Ian Rider nine years.
I didn't know about any of this.

45:02.074 --> 45:04.534
- if anything happens to Alex ...
- It won't.

45:05.494 --> 45:07.412
We'll take care of him, I promise.

45:08.080 --> 45:09.580
By the way, he...

45:10.416 --> 45:14.794
