46:38.670 --> 46:42.173
Kevin?

46:55.687 --> 46:59.148
Here it is, sir. I do hope this
satisfies your requirements.

47:02.820 --> 47:06.280
This is a scale model of the rooftop
at your London HQ.

47:15.707 --> 47:18.918
I've incorporated a powerful
nationwide transmitter...

47:19.169 --> 47:21.671
