- I was lucky. I got out.

49:04.733 --> 49:07.526
My mother won a million dollars on
the state lottery.

49:07.736 --> 49:12.198
she had me educated in the best
schooling system in the world in your country.

49:13.617 --> 49:15.993
- You were at school with the Prime
