01:00:37.175 --> 01:00:40.135
R-5. What is it?

01:00:40.762 --> 01:00:42.512
Put it back.

01:01:01.949 --> 01:01:03.033
The way out.

01:01:04.452 --> 01:01:05.577
Now.

01:02:36.836 --> 01:02:38.420
Going somewhere?

01:02:39.630 --> 01:02:40.714
Kevin?

01:03:07.283 --> 01:03:10.368
